{"tid":721863,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"日本橫傳到完場遭國民鬧爆　網民嘲笑如現實中的星野源","createTime":"2018-06-29T04:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T09:03:15.000Z","uid":36494,"like":148,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"23599bd352f19496fd286cbb70c9729cb0ae2eba","tid":721863,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/121737_7d210c3cd0b520188dc5ff4c25d7da5a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F121737_7d210c3cd0b520188dc5ff4c25d7da5a.png&h=7db725ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c092dad047fcfdae01b21dd31ea32acfaf266c87","tid":721863,"uid":36494,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"雖然日本順利出線，但到最後關頭消極比賽，最終只靠較少黃牌，即較好的公平競技分出線，表現便不獲日本網民接受。首先是日本足總官方Twitter出帖慶祝「藍武士」晉級，卻引來不少人指國家隊欠武士道精神。<br />\n<br />\n最「mean」爆的留言，必數有日本網民以日本國民女神新垣結衣的劇集《逃避雖可恥但有用》，諷刺日本隊如劇中的星野源，於困難時便不斷回避問題。這個「神Tweet」獲得大量網民認同，完場不足1小時便有過萬retweet，令人哭笑不得。未知日本隊如此消極，結衣BB會否為他們打氣？<br />\n<br />\n不過日本中場柴崎岳的未婚妻真野恵里菜，便正正在《逃避雖可恥但有用》中飾演田中安惠一角，日本網民作此比喻亦不為過吧。"},{"pid":"8923ebccdf5f0cba89e32f869676f803fbbf9d74","tid":721863,"uid":2169,"like":65,"dislike":4,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:20:51.000Z","msg":"@祟日撚<br />\n<br />\n佢地係咪又忽然球迷 賭仔 五毛？"},{"pid":"96d05140befa4dc55d7918e1540f373387bec718","tid":721863,"uid":102240,"like":113,"dislike":14,"score":99,"quote":{"pid":"8923ebccdf5f0cba89e32f869676f803fbbf9d74","tid":721863,"uid":2169,"like":65,"dislike":4,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:20:51.000Z","msg":"@祟日撚<br />\n<br />\n佢地係咪又忽然球迷 賭仔 五毛？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T04:23:30.000Z","msg":"連日本仔自己都唔撐<br />\n<br />\n連登崇日child搶住含<img src=\"/a